  • 所有已实现的接口:
    Rule

    public class ConwaysUnderpopulationRule
extends ConwayAbstractRule
    This should implements Conway's rule for under-population: "Any live cell with fewer than two live neighbours dies, as if caused by under-population."
    作者:
    David J. Pearce
